data.description: Darling 3 bed 2 bath manufactured home in the country - complete with Ring doorbell and Backup Generator!  Single-level living and a fully fenced back yard including: Fire Pit & wood for marshmallow roasting, sandbox for the littles, and a garden area to grow your own produce in the summer. Plenty of parking including a concrete parking area.  Master bedroom suite with separate shower and garden tub, including an extra large walk-in closet / den area.  Water your yard with a fully automatic sprinkling system. Spacious, well-designed kitchen. Never go without power with your very own professionally installed back-up generator system which runs 100% of the home (even a/c in summer).  There are custom lighting upgrades as well as Mountain and Valley views. Property located in an un-zoned area; Pets / animals allowed. No HOA. This home/property is ready for you to enjoy for many years to come! This Home is permanently affixed to the foundation and was recorded as such in 2008. Images of info tag and plates (manufactured) are included in listing docs.
